feedback.help_us_improve: Āwhinatia mātou ki te whakapai ake
feedback.help_content_goes_here: Ka noho te ihirangi āwhina ki konei.
feedback.thanks_for_helping_onetime_secret_improv: Ngā mihi mō tō āwhina ki a Onetime Secret ki te whakapai ake. He mea nui tēnei.
feedback.weve_built_this_tool_to_help_you_share_s: Kua hangaia e mātou tēnei taputapu hei āwhina i a koe ki te tuari mōhiohio tairongo i runga i te haumaru, ā, he mea nui ō wheako ao-tūturu mō te arotahi i ā mātou mahi. Ka āwhina i a mātou ki te whakatau he aha te mahi ā muri ake nei me te pēhea te whakapai ake i te ratonga mō te katoa.
feedback.hey_there_thanks_for_stopping_by_our_fee: Tēnā koe, ngā mihi mō tō toro mai ki tā mātou whārangi urupare. Ehara tō kōrero i te mea pōwhiri noa - he mea nui.
feedback.a_note_from_delano_founder_of_onetime_se: He tuhipoka mai i a Delano, kaiwhakarewa o Onetime Secret
